# 💰 Expense Tracker

A modern and responsive **Expense Tracker** built using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. Easily manage your budget, track expenses, and visualize your spending with a clean and user-friendly dashboard.

---

## 📸 Preview



---

## ✨ Features

- 💰 Set and update your budget
- ➕ Add new expenses
- ✏️ Edit existing expenses
- 🗑️ Delete individual expenses
- 🧹 Clear all expense history
- 📊 Real-time budget calculations
- 🥧 Dynamic pie chart visualization
- 💾 LocalStorage support
- 📱 Fully responsive design
- ⚡ Fast and lightweight

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (ES6)
- Font Awesome
- LocalStorage API

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```
Expense-Tracker/
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── script.js
└── README.md
```

---

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/ganesharunpatil/Expense-Tracker.git
```

### 2️⃣ Open the Project Folder

```bash
cd Expense-Tracker
```

### 3️⃣ Run the Project

Simply open **index.html** in your preferred web browser.

---

## 📌 How to Use

1. Enter your budget.
2. Add your expenses with name and amount.
3. Edit or delete expenses anytime.
4. Click **Clear List** to remove all expense history.
5. Your data is automatically saved using **LocalStorage**.

